      "span_text": "In a previous assay, alfentanil recovery from human plasma using Oasis MCX SPE exceeded 80%. [CITATION_1] The recovery of both alfentanil and midazolam extracted simultaneously in this assay was evaluated by comparing the mean peak areas from analyte added to and recovered from the biological matrix (extracted samples) to the peak areas from unextracted samples at three concentrations (1, 10, and 100 ng/ml, n=5 each), as described for the matrix effect test.",
